  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and the Latin was-- although I really don't know more about it too much than I can read naturally the numbers or some of the things in the churches what is written on-- but it was a very, very important influence on me.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For example, Lucius [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Severus ?] was one of the Roman senators.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, at one point, there was a rebel in one of the area in that time in Italy-- which was, of course, not called Italy at that time-- and Rome.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And what it was, the, the people, the so-called plebs, which is nobility versus the plebs-- rebelled.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this senator went to give a talk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the talk was about that [SIGHS] a body was-- the different part of the body is upset about the stomach.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The hands is supposedly made a lot of work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The feet had to go there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The mouth is chewing, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But the stomach doesn't seem to work enough.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So they decided they're not going to feed their stomach.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So-- and then, of course, the consequences is very obvious.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I think this was a very good impact on me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I think that, to me, it is not-- the issue is that who you are and what you do, what-- you have a certain role.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You could say that some of the role is maybe more important for one than for that other.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But the whole thing is like a wheel-- go around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so that we have a specific role in this world, regardless what we are and what our education or responsibility is.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Some of them are more glamorous than others-- like in a air-- let's say air carrier.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Obviously, the pilots has the glamor.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
